B.a1c=new A.dl("Assess obstruction","If they can cough, encourage it. Only act if unable to speak, cough, or breathe.")
B.a0T=new A.dl("Lean forward","Support chest, tilt victim forward so expelled object falls out.")
B.a19=new A.dl("5 back blows","Strike firmly between shoulder blades with heel of hand. 5 separate blows.")
B.a1b=new A.dl("5 abdominal thrusts","Fist above navel. Grasp fist. Pull sharply inward and upward.")
