B.a18=new A.dl("F \u2014 Face","Ask them to smile. Does one side droop? Asymmetry is a warning sign.")
B.a17=new A.dl("A \u2014 Arms","Eyes closed, both arms raised. Does one drift downward?")
B.a0Y=new A.dl("S \u2014 Speech","Repeat a simple phrase. Slurred, strange, or impossible = stroke sign.")
B.a15=new A.dl("T \u2014 Time","Note exact onset time. Call 112 immediately.")
